snippet.title: JUMP FORCE - GAMESCOM 2018 TRAILER | X1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
The battle for Earth intensifies as new enemies threaten our reality. Will you unite with Vegeta, Gon, and Sanji to protect our world? 

JUMP FORCE launches on Xbox One, PS4, and Steam in 2019. Pre-order your copy today: https://bandainam.co/JumpForcePO
